# Component Guidelines

## Structure
- Use functional components with TypeScript
- Implement ARIA roles and accessibility features
- Maximum 300 lines of code per file
- Use Shadcn/ui components as base
- Follow TailwindCSS class naming conventions

## Requirements
- Export default component matching filename
- Include prop interface with JSDoc
- Implement error boundaries for critical operations
- Support mobile-first responsive design
- Use native recording interface for audio components

## State Management
- Prefer hooks for complex state
- Use React.memo for expensive renders
- Implement loading states
- Handle error states gracefully
- Support offline capabilities where relevant

## Styling
- Use TailwindCSS utility classes
- Follow design system color tokens
- Support dark/light modes
- Use CSS variables for theme values
- No inline styles

## Performance
- Lazy load heavy components
- Implement proper suspense boundaries
- Optimize media loading
- Use proper image formats and sizes
- Monitor render cycles 